title: Noble Formula 2% Pyrithione Zinc Bar Soap
description: Noble Formula 2% Pyrithione Zinc Bar Soap - Original Formulawas especially formulated for those with psoriasis, eczema and dry skin, although it is an excellent cleansing bar for any skin type or condition.In addition to pyrithione zinc (ZnP) NF Bar Soap also contains a high percentage of nourishing olive oil, moisturizing emu oil and a gently exfoliating oatmeal.Noble Formula Bar Soap is handmade, hand shaped and may vary slightly in size and shape, but will always equal or exceed 3.25 oz.

title: Burt's Bees Intense Hydration Night Cream, 1.8 Ounces
description: How to determine the expiration date:The lot code is six to seven  digits long and starts with a 0, 1, 2 or 3. To read the lot code, the  first three numbers are the day of the year the product was made (aka  Julian Date). The next two digits are the year, and the last two digits  are a batch number we use internally for identification. For example,  lot code 0400901 translates to a product made on February 9, 2009 from  Batch Number 1.
